<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">春风拂槛，郁金飘香。2026年3月14日，经济管理学院以“春遇芳华，不负美好”为主题，邀请全体师生共赴一场春日手作之约，在传统拓印与趣味游戏中舒展身心、凝聚温情，不负春光与美好。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UEIVGGHOVVA6gSibvpVlnbjMicqhKurAggjyfyKwBKicOlksCSLpgWf1RjEcJ0WuV3Y7ZMesbhOgynB5tZevdnNCdzdS88sjvLP29liatAznWZk/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=5" alt="" data-href="" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837860195.jpg" alt="1773837860195.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837860195.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在拓印体验区，师生们自选“金榜题名”“平安喜乐”“前程似锦”等寓意美好的图案，以传统拓印技艺创作专属手作，完成后装裱入框带走。一压一拓间，传统技艺的魅力悄然流淌，将春日的温柔与对生活的期许永久定格。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837881890.jpg" alt="1773837881890.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837881890.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837912186.jpg" alt="1773837912186.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837912186.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837928856.jpg" alt="1773837928856.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837928856.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837943613.jpg" alt="1773837943613.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837943613.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837956117.jpg" alt="1773837956117.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837956117.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837969440.jpg" alt="1773837969440.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837969440.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837982660.jpg" alt="1773837982660.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837982660.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">套圈区域欢声笑语不断，大家站在指定线外，瞄准地上的精美小礼品，精准抛出手中的塑料圈。套中礼品的雀跃与未中的调侃交织成热闹的氛围，让大家在简单的游戏里找回童年的快乐，收获满满的小确幸。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837995379.jpg" alt="1773837995379.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773837995379.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838016312.jpg" alt="1773838016312.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838016312.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838028826.jpg" alt="1773838028826.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838028826.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838047422.jpg" alt="1773838047422.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838047422.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838060563.jpg" alt="1773838060563.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838060563.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838071744.jpg" alt="1773838071744.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838071744.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在射击区域，参与者手持道具枪，瞄准前方的气球阵列扣动扳机。子弹破空的清脆声响、气球破裂的趣味瞬间，让大家在竞技中释放压力，凭借击破气球的数量兑换相应奖品，体验挑战与收获的双重快乐。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838087357.jpg" alt="1773838087357.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838087357.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838105345.jpg" alt="1773838105345.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838105345.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838122453.jpg" alt="1773838122453.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838122453.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838134227.jpg" alt="1773838134227.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838134227.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838144466.jpg" alt="1773838144466.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838144466.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这场春日活动，是传统技艺与现代趣味的碰撞，也是学院温情关怀的传递。未来，经济管理学院将继续策划更多有温度、有意义的活动，让师生们在丰富的体验中感受生活之美、凝聚集体力量，共赴更多美好时光。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838177833.jpg" alt="1773838177833.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838177833.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838193742.jpg" alt="1773838193742.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838193742.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838204715.jpg" alt="1773838204715.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838204715.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838215722.jpg" alt="1773838215722.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773838215722.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p>